@host = http://localhost:5099

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Search — dense/noisy query
POST {{host}}/api/books/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "tolkien hobbit illustrated deluxe 1937"
}

### Search — ambiguous character hint
POST {{host}}/api/books/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mark huckleberry"
}

### Search — author only
POST {{host}}/api/books/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "dickens"
}

### Search — validation error (empty query -> 400)
POST {{host}}/api/books/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": ""
}
